        "This initiative, part of a broader plan to extend coverage across the entire Tube and London Overground network, aims to improve connectivity.[110] Honours and awards In 2024, the Elizabeth line won the RIBA London Street of the Year award,[111] and won the Stirling Prize for the same year.[112] Muyiwa Oki, RIBA president and chair of judges, said the Elizabeth line was \"a triumph in architect-led collaboration\" that transformed \"the typical commuter chaos ." .

